    "3d4b17e0-df51-4532-9672-5bed16d609c7": {
      "id": "3d4b17e0-df51-4532-9672-5bed16d609c7",
      "name": "Executive Summary",
      "content": "<p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Transform IdiamPro from a standalone outlining application into an AI-native platform with full programmatic access via Model Context Protocol (MCP). This plan covers technical architecture, implementation phases, and commercialization strategy.</p><p>**Key Decisions:**<br>- **Target Market**: Hybrid (start with developers/prosumers, expand to enterprise)<br>- **Integration**: MCP server integrated into IdiamPro app (GUI + API access)<br>- **Monetization**: Open source core + paid premium features<br>- **Launch**: Soft launch MCP in beta first, before main product</p><p>---</p>",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "0b4b1874-027a-4b81-9918-1c126b9e6619",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "1",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "ffb32da6-e917-4e8c-b55d-ec7ef66fa047": {
      "id": "ffb32da6-e917-4e8c-b55d-ec7ef66fa047",
      "name": "Technical Architecture",
      "content": "<p></p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "0b4b1874-027a-4b81-9918-1c126b9e6619",
      "childrenIds": [
        "b51c20cd-b7f3-439a-9c08-53950ec12450",
        "6a24eb92-1979-4c86-9390-8ff517f33644"
      ],
      "prefix": "2",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "b51c20cd-b7f3-439a-9c08-53950ec12450": {
      "id": "b51c20cd-b7f3-439a-9c08-53950ec12450",
      "name": "MCP Server Structure",
      "content": "**Implementation:**\n- Standalone TypeScript MCP server using `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk`\n- Runs as separate Node.js process (local or containerized)\n- Connects to IdiamPro's existing storage layer\n\n**Directory Structure:**\n```\n/mcp-server/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 src/\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 index.ts              # Server entry point\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 server.ts             # MCP server setup\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 tools/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 free/             # Open source tools\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 outline-read.ts\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 outline-crud.ts\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 node-crud.ts\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 tag-ops.ts\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 premium/          # Paid features\n\u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 ai-generate.ts\n\u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 ai-ingest.ts\n\u2502   \u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 bulk-ops.ts\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 auth/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 api-key-manager.ts\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 plan-checker.ts\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 storage/\n\u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 storage-factory.ts\n```",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "ffb32da6-e917-4e8c-b55d-ec7ef66fa047",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "2.1",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "6a24eb92-1979-4c86-9390-8ff517f33644": {
      "id": "6a24eb92-1979-4c86-9390-8ff517f33644",
      "name": "Integration with Existing Code",
      "content": "**Shared Library Strategy:**\n- Create `@idiampro/core` package with:\n  - Type definitions (OutlineNode, NodeMap, Outline)\n  - Core utilities (outline-utils, tag-utils)\n  - Storage interfaces\n- Both Next.js app and MCP server import from shared package\n\n**Authentication Flow:**\n```\nUser generates API Key in IdiamPro GUI\n  \u2192 Key stored with plan tier (FREE/PREMIUM/PRO/ENTERPRISE)\n  \u2192 MCP Client sends key in headers\n  \u2192 Server validates and enforces plan limits\n```\n\n**Supported Transports:**\n1. **stdio** - Claude Desktop (primary)\n2. **SSE** - Web-based clients\n3. **HTTP** - REST integrations (future)\n\n---",
      "type": "code",
      "parentId": "ffb32da6-e917-4e8c-b55d-ec7ef66fa047",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "2.2",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63": {
      "id": "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63",
      "name": "MCP Tool Design",
      "content": "",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "0b4b1874-027a-4b81-9918-1c126b9e6619",
      "childrenIds": [
        "7fe53a97-b423-442d-8046-d8d087ab9072",
        "b436bdcc-6046-400e-a86d-80f25683da44",
        "3b8567b3-c3d9-42ad-aa22-88d7383299f2",
        "0c8610c8-45ae-4d9e-a6c2-09c90c962546"
      ],
      "prefix": "3",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "7fe53a97-b423-442d-8046-d8d087ab9072": {
      "id": "7fe53a97-b423-442d-8046-d8d087ab9072",
      "name": "Free Tier Tools (Open Source - MIT License)",
      "content": "**Read Operations:**\n- `list_outlines` - List all outlines with metadata\n- `get_outline` - Get complete outline by ID/name\n- `get_node` - Get specific node with context\n- `search_nodes` - Full-text search across nodes\n\n**Basic CRUD:**\n- `create_node` - Add node to tree\n- `update_node` - Modify node properties\n- `delete_node` - Remove node and children\n- `move_node` - Reorder tree structure\n\n**Tag Operations:**\n- `add_tag` - Tag a node\n- `remove_tag` - Remove tag\n- `list_tags` - Get all tags\n- `filter_by_tags` - Find tagged nodes\n\n**Limits:** 1,000 API calls/month",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "3.1",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "b436bdcc-6046-400e-a86d-80f25683da44": {
      "id": "b436bdcc-6046-400e-a86d-80f25683da44",
      "name": "Premium Tier Tools (Proprietary)",
      "content": "**AI-Powered Operations:**\n- `generate_outline` - Create outline from topic (100/month)\n- `expand_content` - Generate node content (500/month)\n- `ingest_source` - Import YouTube/PDF/text (50/month)\n\n**Bulk Operations:**\n- `batch_update_nodes` - Update multiple nodes atomically\n- `multi_select_action` - Bulk tag, color, move operations\n\n**Limits:** 10,000 API calls/month\n\n**Implementation Example:**\n```typescript\n// Premium tool with plan checking\n{\n  name: \"generate_outline\",\n  description: \"Generate outline from topic using AI (PREMIUM)\",\n  handler: async (args, apiKey) => {\n    const plan = await auth.getPlanForKey(apiKey);\n    if (plan === 'FREE') {\n      throw new Error('Requires PREMIUM plan');\n    }\n    return await generateOutlineAction(args.topic);\n  }\n}\n```",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "3.2",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036242,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036242
      }
    },
    "3b8567b3-c3d9-42ad-aa22-88d7383299f2": {
      "id": "3b8567b3-c3d9-42ad-aa22-88d7383299f2",
      "name": "Pro Tier (Future)",
      "content": "- Unlimited AI operations\n- Semantic search\n- Cross-outline queries\n- Priority support\n- 50,000 API calls/month",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "3.3",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "0c8610c8-45ae-4d9e-a6c2-09c90c962546": {
      "id": "0c8610c8-45ae-4d9e-a6c2-09c90c962546",
      "name": "Enterprise Tier (Future)",
      "content": "- Team collaboration features\n- SSO and advanced security\n- Audit logs\n- Custom integrations\n- On-premise deployment\n\n---",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "4a22e316-cf46-44b8-89bd-b41e1e4d4b63",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "3.4",
