    "ea74d226-353f-4239-a252-6e7efc40b017": {
      "id": "ea74d226-353f-4239-a252-6e7efc40b017",
      "name": "Phase 1: Core MCP Server - BETA (Weeks 1-4)",
      "content": "**Week 1-2: Foundation**\n- Set up MCP server project structure\n- Implement storage adapters (reuse existing storage-manager.ts)\n- Create API key authentication system\n- Basic stdio transport for Claude Desktop\n\n**Week 2-3: Free Tier Tools**\n- Implement all read operations\n- Implement basic CRUD (create, update, delete, move nodes)\n- Implement tag operations\n- Write comprehensive tests\n\n**Week 3-4: Beta Testing**\n- Package for npm distribution\n- Write documentation and setup guide\n- Onboard 10-20 beta testers\n- Gather feedback and iterate\n\n**Success Criteria:**\n- Server runs stably with Claude Desktop\n- All free tier tools work reliably\n- Beta testers successfully integrate\n- Documentation covers common use cases",
      "type": "task",
      "parentId": "3ce6cda2-ed3a-4467-83de-41a361540e46",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "4.1",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "d2fe692c-4710-4bd6-a800-f4fd8e60659a": {
      "id": "d2fe692c-4710-4bd6-a800-f4fd8e60659a",
      "name": "Phase 2: Premium AI Tools (Weeks 5-7)",
      "content": "**Week 5: AI Integration**\n- Integrate existing AI service (ai-service.ts, actions.ts)\n- Implement generate_outline tool\n- Implement expand_content tool\n- Plan-based access control\n\n**Week 6: Advanced AI Features**\n- Implement ingest_source (YouTube, PDF extraction)\n- Context-aware content generation\n- Optimize AI prompts for MCP context\n\n**Week 7: Testing & Refinement**\n- Test with premium beta users\n- Optimize response times\n- Implement rate limiting\n- Premium feature documentation\n\n**Success Criteria:**\n- AI operations work seamlessly\n- Premium feature gating works correctly\n- Response times < 10s for AI operations",
      "type": "task",
      "parentId": "3ce6cda2-ed3a-4467-83de-41a361540e46",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "4.2",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "8a331195-c424-4c5f-a51e-d36b37ed6226": {
      "id": "8a331195-c424-4c5f-a51e-d36b37ed6226",
      "name": "Phase 3: Advanced Features (Weeks 8-10)",
      "content": "**Week 8: Bulk Operations**\n- Implement batch_update_nodes\n- Implement multi_select_action\n- Transaction support for atomic operations\n\n**Week 9: SSE Transport**\n- Add SSE for web clients\n- Simple web MCP client demo\n- Security hardening\n\n**Week 10: Polish**\n- Performance optimization\n- Error handling improvements\n- Logging and debugging tools\n- Final documentation\n\n**Success Criteria:**\n- Bulk operations handle 100+ nodes\n- SSE transport works\n- Production-ready",
      "type": "task",
      "parentId": "3ce6cda2-ed3a-4467-83de-41a361540e46",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "4.3",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "30a3de61-ab03-448a-a158-dfd4b2c2f80f": {
      "id": "30a3de61-ab03-448a-a158-dfd4b2c2f80f",
      "name": "Phase 4: Enterprise (Weeks 11-14) - Future",
      "content": "- Real-time collaboration\n- SSO integration (OAuth2, SAML)\n- Role-based access control\n- Advanced analytics\n\n---",
      "type": "task",
      "parentId": "3ce6cda2-ed3a-4467-83de-41a361540e46",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "4.4",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
