    "30980a13-7b58-4230-8e6e-2a7c1686ce7d": {
      "id": "30980a13-7b58-4230-8e6e-2a7c1686ce7d",
      "name": "Open Source Strategy",
      "content": "**Licensing:**\n- **Free Tier**: MIT License (fully open source)\n  - GitHub: `idiampro/idiampro-mcp-server`\n  - Encourage community contributions\n  - Build trust and adoption\n\n- **Premium Tier**: Proprietary (source-available for inspection)\n  - OR dual-license: AGPL for self-hosted, commercial for SaaS\n\n**Repositories:**\n```\ngithub.com/idiampro/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 idiampro-mcp-server        # Free tools (open source)\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 idiampro-mcp-premium       # Premium plugin\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 idiampro-core              # Shared utilities (MIT)\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 idiampro-examples          # Integration examples\n```",
      "type": "chapter",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.1",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "dd37675e-7382-429f-88c3-31129138adb1": {
      "id": "dd37675e-7382-429f-88c3-31129138adb1",
      "name": "Pricing Structure",
      "content": "| Tier | Price | Features | API Calls | Target |\n|------|-------|----------|-----------|---------|\n| **Free** | $0 | Read ops, basic CRUD, tags, search | 1,000/mo | Developers, hobbyists |\n| **Premium** | $19/mo ($15 annual) | + AI generation (100/mo), AI expansion (500/mo), ingestion (50/mo), bulk ops | 10,000/mo | Professional users, consultants |\n| **Pro** | $49/mo ($39 annual) | + Unlimited AI, semantic search, cross-outline queries | 50,000/mo | Small teams, agencies |\n| **Enterprise** | Custom | + Team collab, SSO, audit logs, on-premise | Custom | Large organizations |",
      "type": "spreadsheet",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.2",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "138750c2-8b90-4972-b378-a86890dd26c8": {
      "id": "138750c2-8b90-4972-b378-a86890dd26c8",
      "name": "Developer Onboarding",
      "content": "**Documentation:**\n1. **Quick Start** (5 minutes to first API call)\n   - Install via npm\n   - Configure Claude Desktop\n   - Make first request\n\n2. **API Reference**\n   - Tool catalog with examples\n   - Schema documentation\n   - Error codes and best practices\n\n3. **Integration Guides**\n   - Claude Desktop setup\n   - VS Code integration\n   - Custom MCP client development\n   - Workflow automation\n\n4. **Video Tutorials**\n   - \"Building with IdiamPro MCP\" series\n   - Weekly live coding sessions\n   - Community showcases\n\n**Developer Portal:**\n- API key generation/management\n- Usage dashboard (calls, limits)\n- Plan upgrade/downgrade\n- Billing and support",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.3",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "0e325898-20ba-4e2c-8529-49eccda60ca7": {
      "id": "0e325898-20ba-4e2c-8529-49eccda60ca7",
      "name": "Marketing Messaging",
      "content": "**Value Proposition:**\n\"IdiamPro: The AI-Native Outliner with Full API Access\"\n\n**Key Messages:**\n1. **Developers**: \"Integrate powerful outlining into your workflow\"\n2. **Power Users**: \"Automate knowledge management with AI\"\n3. **Teams**: \"Collaborate on structured content programmatically\"\n\n**Content Marketing:**\n\n**Blog Posts:**\n- \"Building an AI Outline Generator with MCP\"\n- \"Automating Research with IdiamPro and Claude\"\n- \"From YouTube to Outline in 60 Seconds\"\n- \"10 MCP Workflows for Knowledge Workers\"\n\n**Example Projects (Open Source):**\n- Chrome extension: Save web pages as outline nodes\n- Obsidian plugin: Sync between Obsidian and IdiamPro\n- Slack bot: Create outlines from Slack threads\n- Email parser: Convert emails to outlines\n\n**Social Media:**\n- Twitter: Code snippets, tips, community highlights\n- YouTube: Tutorial series, demos\n- Dev.to: Technical deep-dives\n- Reddit: r/productivity, r/AI, r/programming",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.4",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "d7c6397c-43ba-4a5f-89ec-512ca4fd4de5": {
      "id": "d7c6397c-43ba-4a5f-89ec-512ca4fd4de5",
      "name": "Distribution Channels",
      "content": "**Primary:**\n1. **MCP Registry** (modelcontextprotocol.io) - Official listing\n2. **npm** - `npm install -g @idiampro/mcp-server`\n3. **GitHub Marketplace** - Featured MCP implementation\n4. **Product Hunt** - Launch with v1.0\n5. **Claude Desktop** - Pre-configured template\n\n**Partnerships:**\n- Anthropic: Featured case study\n- Obsidian: Note-taking integration\n- DevTool companies: Bundled offerings",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.5",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "262dc1a9-25b1-4483-9d93-e2ce219d4dc7": {
      "id": "262dc1a9-25b1-4483-9d93-e2ce219d4dc7",
      "name": "Go-to-Market Timeline",
      "content": "**Weeks 1-4: Beta**\n- 50 beta testers\n- Feedback surveys\n- Bug reports\n- 3-5 case studies/testimonials\n\n**Weeks 5-6: Soft Launch**\n- Public GitHub repo\n- npm package\n- Documentation site (docs.idiampro.com/mcp)\n- Initial blog post\n\n**Weeks 7-8: Full Launch**\n- Product Hunt\n- MCP Registry submission\n- Press release\n- Social media campaign\n- Launch webinar\n\n**Weeks 9-12: Growth**\n- Weekly content\n- Community building (Discord)\n- Partnership outreach\n- Feature releases\n\n**Month 4+: Scale**\n- Premium tier launch\n- Enterprise pilots\n- Conference talks\n- Influencer partnerships\n\n---",
      "type": "note",
      "parentId": "6f68576a-8b86-4257-9eee-dacdef63c314",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "prefix": "5.6",
      "metadata": {
        "createdAt": 1768038036243,
        "updatedAt": 1768038036243
      }
    },
    "ca18f73a-6dde-4a3e-9b63-87fbc375f67f": {
      "id": "ca18f73a-6dde-4a3e-9b63-87fbc375f67f",
      "name": "Key Metrics & Success Criteria",
      "content": "",
      "type": "spreadsheet",
      "parentId": "0b4b1874-027a-4b81-9918-1c126b9e6619",
      "childrenIds": [
        "2258dfd6-cad5-422a-bdd3-6a0f60049028",
